INSERT INTO
                    url_results (id, provider_id, client_id, result_type, working_url, retrievability_percent, result_code, error_code, tested_at)
               SELECT
                    UNNEST($1::uuid[]),
                    UNNEST($2::text[]),
                    UNNEST($3::text[]),
                    UNNEST($4::text[]),
                    UNNEST($5::text[]),
                    UNNEST($6::double precision[]),
                    UNNEST($7::text[]),
                    UNNEST($8::text[]),
                    UNNEST($9::timestamptz[])
